snippet.title: Skulldash Expansion Pack - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Development is finally coming to a close! With only a few weeks left until the release date it seemed appropriate to get the announcement trailer done.

Skulldash will be released for GZDoom on the 22nd October, 2017. Get ready to play the enhanced version of the Cacoward winning Fast-Paced Speedrun Arcade Mod For Doom II, complete with 15+ new levels made from members of the community!

Doomworld Thread:
https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/96735-skulldash-expansion-release-date-announced/

Watch the development streams:
https://www.twitch.tv/dragonflyos

Join the Discord:
https://discord.gg/TCwH4DP
